messages.text: Are you free to talk yet? My parents are such narks for freaking out over us having a little fun.
I am babes. And don’t even get me started.
It was like I was being grounded and forced into a pit in the ground for hanging with my best friend.
omg V you are so funny.
Are you coming with me to school tmrw then since you are out of being suspended from basically all things involving my life.
Lol And I’m glad you’re back. Can you believe they took away my phone?
Mos Def. We will just have to be low key about it. And yeah I’m surprised that’s all they did.
Sweet. I’m going to bed now, but I’ll meet up with you by the bus stop like before okay?
:) Sounds good.
a few hours later
V Are you awake? I know it’s pretty late.
Yeah dude it’s 3 am. What is it?
I keep hearing things.
People spreading rumors or something? Dude ignore that. We can talk about it later.
No. Right now I keep hearing things.
Like scraping. Nails on the chalk board sort of thing.
Outside your house? Maybe it’s a deer or your brother sneaking in late or something.
No V. It’s in my room.
Okay I’m seriously awake now. Well get up and turn on the light. You’re already on your phone.
I’m too afraid.
It’s okay. Just use the light on the back of your phone and shine it around.
What if something comes charging at me?
Really Lena? This isn’t Paranormal Activity okay.
Okay I turned on my lamp.
And?
Nothing.
Okay so let’s BOTH go back to sleep.
Sorry V.
It’s fine. Leave your TV on but put it on mute. It’ll give you light so you won’t go to sleep in the complete dark.
Thanks. Goodnight.
Night.
V. My TV turned off.
WTF!? Dude please you probably rolled over on the remote or something.
No it turned off and then I heard it again. It sounded like someone was near it.
Okay tell your parents. I can’t do anything.
Make it stop V please.
It’s your imagination. What do you want me to do?
They’re writing on the walls.
In blood
Okay you’re obviously doing this just to F with me.
No. It says…she’s back.
Tell your parents!!! Show them then!
V when I read your text to show my parents I heard my door lock.
Dude. Call them. Scream!!
I feel it V. It’s next to me.
What? Shine the light on it like I told you. Stand up for yourself or something.
Against a demon?!? This is what my dad said would happen if I didn’t go to Church more.
The only reason I won’t roll my eyes is because I’m slightly freaked right now.
The light on my phone isn’t working. My lamp isn’t even working.
How is that possible? Is it plugged in?
Okay I ran to the bathroom in my room. The lights are fine in here.
Did you check behind the shower curtain?
Are you trying to make this worse? Yes. I checked there!
Lena I am going to ask you something and I need a serious answer the first time. I have very little patience. Especially at 4 am.
No I’m not making this crap up.
Are you the one that started taking your pills again to get rid of me?
What? How would pills get rid of you?
Maybe I didn’t make myself clear.
V! It followed me in here. The mirror is getting steamy and it’s getting hard to breathe. It’s writing something on the mirror.
Read it and do as it says.
It says answer me.
Then do it. I won’t repeat myself.
You? You’re playing a prank on me?
Do you think the amount of oxygen in a room being reduced while you’re in it is a prank? Why did you let them take you to that place to help you think I wasn’t real?
I’m sorry. V! I’m just starting to remember bits and pieces.
Well remember it all. We had fun. We were friends. I was always there with you and you let them try to kill me.
Veronica stop it.
No! Do you want to know what it feels like?
I’m sorry for whatever I did. Really I am. Just make it stop. It’s so foggy I can’t see. It’s so thick. I can feel someone touching me, but I can’t get of them.
That’s how I felt.
The glass just broke. How do I make it stop?
You can’t this time.
I’ll pray. That never fails.
It’s not that easy with me little Lena. I am in you.
I’m nothing like you.
You seem afraid down there on the floor.
I just took my pills. I remember now. You’ll be gone when I wake up from this.
the next morning
Are you up now sweet pea? It’s time for school?
Where am I? Where did you take me?
Oh I didn’t take you anywhere. We just switched places.
What do you mean? It’s so dark here. I feel like I’m barely in my own body…I’m just watching from the inside.
That’s right. You’re going to start to feel a lot smaller as I take over.
But I took my pills.
News flash sweetie. It has to be on a consistent basis. You missed two weeks of them.
Please don’t do this V. Let me out. My parents will know something is wrong with my personality.
Not if they’re not around...
Please. What is this?
Still confused? We’re one in the same.
Different personalities. One body. Think about it little Lena
Your parents never gave you that phone back. How could you have been texting me?
So I’m crazy?
No worries. I’m getting stronger. Pretty soon there won’t be a you. Just me.
